name: jquery-autocomplete

scripts.newversion: npm version patch --no-git-tag-version && npm run newversiongit && npm publish ./
scripts.newversiongit: git add --all  && git commit -m "New version %npm_package_version%. Read more https://github.com/xdan/autocomplete/releases/tag/%npm_package_version% " && git tag %npm_package_version% && git push --tags origin HEAD:master
